title: *PATREON PREVIEW* AMA: The Throwing Fits Biopic Pt. II
description:
The Core Four return to the hot seat, answering your questions in the finale of our latest AMA. Topics include, but are not limited to: thick thighs, Twitch, inspiration for the ears of the front of the face, Jimmy vs. Larry, loafers vs. lace ups, grooming essentials, living in an unfashionable city, financial and career advice, socialism, dressing for the boys, the TF biopic soundtrack and much more on this Patreon-exclusive boyz only edition of The Only Podcast That Matters™.
 
For more Throwing Fits, check us out on Patreon: www.patreon.com/throwingfits
